text.tspan: Built on the highly scalable Linux Kernel and its portable
and vibrant userspace, AOSC OS is ready for your single-
board computers, laptops, desktops, and servers.
Configured for full feature sets, AOSC OS readies your new
and old devices and peripherals for maximal functionality.
Proprietary drivers needed? No problem! With our liberal
software support policies, if your hardware vendors let us,
we will ship them for you.
